textAnnotations.description:
EVEN MY HATEFUL,
XENOPHOBIC, TOTALITARIAN
RHETORIC SOUNDS KIND
OF PRESIDENTIAL!
'M TERRIFIC AT READING
THE TELEPROMPTER... THE
BEST THERE EVER WAS
BELIEVE ME.
(92017
